{"tid":316313,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係用緊SSHD","createTime":"2017-07-10T15:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T04:45:41.000Z","uid":168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81f82a290bb15f5146a63e29445e720ae1dc3062","tid":316313,"uid":168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:36:01.000Z","msg":"雖然好似出咗幾年，但係都好似好少見人討論，<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6iBhf8rpobo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6iBhf8rpobo&d=QLHl5Z7mYCo8Y3dX70CtkJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=99685c8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6iBhf8rpobo</a><br />\n就咁睇個速度SSHD 同SSD 又唔會差好遠，<br />\n價錢又平咁多，點解好似唔覺好多人用?"},{"pid":"73d3fbafd1397e25cf7eb5565f51d21fe33b7723","tid":316313,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:38:41.000Z","msg":"因為hybrid易死囉～"},{"pid":"ebd2c4cbae86d51c7899f9e4112a12a34a7f3cf3","tid":316313,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"佢定位唔高又唔低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSSD技術進步快過hard disk<br />\n而且唔少SSD廠免費送SSD cache software"},{"pid":"df41fd2e3936790b97c36a6b5e76ec127442c8a4","tid":316313,"uid":168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為hybrid易死囉～</blockquote><br />\n願聞其詳，上過其他討論區睇過啲人話好似ssd咁易死，但係佢運作原理又唔似ssd，所以有啲疑問"},{"pid":"b3d11319cff8109d3481d70713f07b5c0c832c83","tid":316313,"uid":168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢定位唔高又唔低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSSD技術進步快過hard disk<br />\n而且唔少SSD廠免費送SSD cache software</blockquote><br />\n佢定位似係平價ssd但係又有速度嘅hdd, 其實都有個優勢喺度"},{"pid":"0f1458363873195422c0b82fdd95a6a013be11c1","tid":316313,"uid":60009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢定位唔高又唔低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSSD技術進步快過hard disk<br />\n而且唔少SSD廠免費送SSD cache software</blockquote><br />\n佢定位似係平價ssd但係又有速度嘅hdd, 其實都有個優勢喺度</blockquote><br />\n期實佢都係想係兩者取平衡啫<br />\n我曾經諗過買隻2tb放落ps4<br />\n但香港好似好少地方賣"},{"pid":"59e55d6a3c7494dc263721146de25441463945f2","tid":316313,"uid":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢定位唔高又唔低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSSD技術進步快過hard disk<br />\n而且唔少SSD廠免費送SSD cache software</blockquote><br />\n佢定位似係平價ssd但係又有速度嘅hdd, 其實都有個優勢喺度</blockquote><br />\n咁我直接用隻SSD裝program,HDD裝DATA仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSSHD 開program唔夠SSD快<br />\n而裝DATA又唔需要咁快"},{"pid":"4862795dd8a7f5bdd6839bf472de847b19a3facf","tid":316313,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:39:45.000Z","msg":"分開 ssd 裝os 同軟件<br />\nhdd 擺data同bt好過啦"},{"pid":"ce711f3e1c9abaad361c1845086da215acca76d6","tid":316313,"uid":168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T04:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分開 ssd 裝os 同軟件<br />\nhdd 擺data同bt好過啦</blockquote><br />\n明明只係平過hdd 少少，但係又平過ssd 咁多，<br />\n係唔明點解好似都係咁少人用啫"},{"pid":"87857198bd640a3561edfc4ba5aca2cafa1738b4","tid":316313,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"用緊openssh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ee1df109b3a67fdd4013ca51314d2a6a32f134","tid":316313,"uid":42802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T04:45:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊openssh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都以為係果個sshd<br />\n利申:最近學緊redhat"}]}